    CLAW HUB - DEATH BALL SCRIPT (UNIVERSAL)
    Fitur:
    1. Auto Parry (Otomatis memblokir bola)
    2. Auto Spam (Serangan otomatis)
    3. Auto Curve (Belokan otomatis)
    4. Aim Assist (Mengarah ke musuh)
    5. GUI dengan tombol minimize
]]

-- // ========== SERVICE & VARIABLE ==========
